              Fires before input is committed to the DOM. Allows you to prevent or modify the default behavior. Browser support varies by version.
            </p>
            <pre
              style="
                background: #f9fafb;
                border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                padding: 1rem;
